<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='580000' id='t-580000'>From the moment that our ancestors,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='583000' id='t-583000'>perhaps two and a half million years ago or so,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='585000' id='t-585000'>began imitating, there was a new copying process.</span>
