11:57
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='706000' id='t-706000'>But that's not all.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='708000' id='t-708000'>We have a new kind of memes now.</span>
