<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='830000' id='t-830000'>I think that's the wrong way to think about it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='834000' id='t-834000'>Intelligence appears all over the place, in all kinds of guises.</span>
